{
  "info": {
    "name": "Samaj Connect API",
    "description": "Backend API for Samaj Connect community app. Phases A-F complete.\n\n## Quick start\n1. Make sure the server is running: `npm run dev` in `server/` (defaults to http://localhost:4000)\n2. Send **Auth → 1. Start (phone lookup)** with `{{phone}}` → confirms the number exists.\n3. Send **Auth → 2. Send OTP** to put the mock code in the dev console.\n4. Send **Auth → 3. Verify OTP** — the test script auto-saves the JWT to `{{token}}`. Every other request uses that token.\n5. To test admin-only endpoints, run `npx tsx scripts/promote.ts 9428656090 ADMIN` from the server folder, then re-login.\n\n## Collection variables\n- `baseUrl` — server URL (default `http://localhost:4000`)\n- `token` — JWT, auto-set by `/auth/verify-otp`\n- `phone` — `9428656090` (logged-in user)\n- `otherPhone` — `8780873706` (second test user)\n- `email` — `pdaksh163@gmail.com`\n- `eventId`, `personId`, `correctionId`, `helpId`, `paymentId`, `expenseId`, `registrationId`, `performanceId` — fill in from response payloads as you go.\n\nMOCK_OTP=true in `.env` makes the verify code always `123456`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "phone", "value": "9428656090", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "otherPhone", "value": "8780873706", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "pdaksh163@gmail.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "eventId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "personId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "householdId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "correctionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "helpId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "expenseId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "registrationId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "performanceId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Start (phone lookup)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{phone}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/start", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "start"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Send OTP (first time: include email)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{phone}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "First login: include email (it's stored on the Person). Subsequent logins can omit email — server reuses the stored one.\n\nWith MOCK_OTP=true the code printed in the server console is always `123456`.",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/send-otp", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "send-otp"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Verify OTP (auto-saves JWT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token);",
                  "    console.log('[Samaj] token saved');",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (j.personId) pm.collectionVariables.set('personId', j.personId);",
                  "  if (j.householdId) pm.collectionVariables.set('householdId', j.householdId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{phone}}\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "verify-otp"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
